# Medical Imaging AI Platform

[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/tumor-detection-segmentation.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/py/tumor-detection-segmentation)
[![Python 3.8+](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.8+-blue.svg)](https://www.python.org/downloads/)
[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)
[![Docker](https://img.shields.io/badge/docker-%230db7ed.svg?style=flat&logo=docker&logoColor=white)](https://hub.docker.com/)

âœ… **PRODUCTION READY** | ğŸ¥ **CLINICAL DEPLOYMENT COMPLETE** | ğŸ¯ **9-STEP WORKFLOW IMPLEMENTED** | ğŸ“¦ **AVAILABLE ON PyPI**

An advanced, production-ready tumor detection and segmentation platform featuring state-of-the-art AI models, multi-modal fusion architectures, neural architecture search, and comprehensive experiment tracking. Built with MONAI, MLflow, and Docker for clinical deployment.

## ğŸš€ Quick Installation

```bash
# Install from PyPI
pip install tumor-detection-segmentation

# Or with all features
pip install tumor-detection-segmentation[all]
```

## ï¿½ Clinical Integration Status

> **âœ… CLINICAL OPERATOR COMPLETE**: Full 9-step clinical workflow automation implemented and tested!
> **ğŸš€ DEPLOYMENT READY**: Launch clinical platform with `./scripts/clinical/run_clinical_operator.sh`
> **ğŸ“Š REAL DATASET TRAINING**: MSD Task01 BrainTumour integrated with UNETR multi-modal training
> **ğŸ›ï¸ HYPERPARAMETER SWEEPS**: Grid search capabilities with MLflow tracking ready
> **ğŸ—ï¸ PROFESSIONALLY ORGANIZED**: Clean project structure with proper file organization

## ï¿½ğŸŒŸ Key Features

- **ğŸ§  Advanced AI Architectures**: UNETR, SegResNet, DiNTS neural architecture search
- **ğŸ”„ Multi-Modal Fusion**: Cross-attention mechanisms for T1/T1c/T2/FLAIR/CT/PET processing
- **ğŸ¯ Cascade Detection Pipeline**: Two-stage detection and segmentation workflow
- **ğŸ¤– Neural Architecture Search (NAS)**: Automated model optimization with DiNTS
- **ğŸ“Š Interactive Annotation**: MONAI Label server with 3D Slicer integration
- **ğŸ“ˆ Experiment Tracking**: MLflow integration with medical imaging metrics
- **ğŸ³ Production Ready**: Complete Docker deployment with GPU acceleration
- **ğŸ¨ Web Interface**: Beautiful dashboard for all platform interactions
- **âš¡ GPU Accelerated**: CUDA and ROCm support with automatic CPU fallback
- **ğŸ¥ Clinical Workflow**: Complete 9-step clinical deployment automation
- **ğŸ›ï¸ Hyperparameter Optimization**: Grid search with concurrent execution
- **ğŸ¯ Real Dataset Integration**: MSD datasets with automated downloading

> **ğŸ³ Docker Deployment Ready**: Complete containerized deployment with web GUI, MLflow tracking, and MONAI Label integration. Launch everything with `./run.sh start`

## ğŸ¥ Clinical Deployment Ready

The platform now includes a **complete clinical integration workflow** that automates the entire deployment process from environment setup to clinical sign-off:

### ğŸš€ Quick Clinical Deployment

```bash
# Complete 9-step clinical workflow automation
./scripts/clinical/run_clinical_operator.sh

# Services will be available at:
# - GUI: http://localhost:8000/gui
# - MLflow: http://localhost:5001
# - MONAI Label: http://localhost:8001/info/
# - API Health: http://localhost:8000/health
```

### ğŸ“‹ 9-Step Clinical Workflow

| Step | Component | Description | Status |
|------|-----------|-------------|--------|
| **1** | Bootstrap | Environment & container verification | âœ… Complete |
| **2** | Virtual Environment | Local development setup | âœ… Complete |
| **3** | Real Dataset | MSD Task01 BrainTumour download | âœ… Complete |
| **4** | Training Config | Hardware-optimized configuration | âœ… Complete |
| **5** | Training Launch | UNETR multi-modal training with MLflow | âœ… Complete |
| **6** | Monitoring | Training progress and system health | âœ… Complete |
| **7** | Inference | Clinical QA overlay generation | âœ… Complete |
| **8** | Clinical Onboarding | Clinical data workflow setup | âœ… Complete |
| **9** | Documentation | Baseline documentation and sign-off | âœ… Complete |

### ğŸ›ï¸ Hyperparameter Optimization

**Grid Search Capabilities** with hardware auto-detection:

```bash
# Large GPU (48GB+): High-resolution training
python scripts/training/launch_expanded_training.py \
  --config config/recipes/unetr_multimodal.json \
  --dataset-config config/datasets/msd_task01_brain.json \
  --grid "roi=160,192 batch_size=4,6 cache=cache amp=true" \
  --epochs 50 --experiment-name msd-task01-unetr-mm-large-gpu

# CPU Only: Optimized for development
python scripts/training/launch_expanded_training.py \
  --config config/recipes/unetr_multimodal.json \
  --dataset-config config/datasets/msd_task01_brain.json \
  --grid "roi=64,96 batch_size=1 cache=smart amp=false" \
  --epochs 50 --experiment-name msd-task01-unetr-mm-cpu
```

**Hardware Auto-Detection:**

- **Large GPU (48GB+)**: ROI 160Â³, Batch 4, Full caching
- **Medium GPU (16-24GB)**: ROI 128Â³, Batch 2, Smart caching
- **Small GPU (8-12GB)**: ROI 96Â³, Batch 1, Smart caching
- **CPU Only**: ROI 64Â³, Batch 1, Smart caching

